@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xysywt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.81 + (v2 + 0.15 * v0 + 0.22)) - v1)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.55) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.20)) + wp.cos(v2))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.98 + v0 + 0.61)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos(v0))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.48 + v0 + 0.34)))
    v0 = 0.50
    data[tid] = v0
